# Mathematics for AI & Machine Learning Mastery

This document outlines the essential mathematical topics required for a deep understanding and mastery of Artificial Intelligence (AI), Machine Learning (ML), Deep Learning (DL), Natural Language Processing (NLP), and Agentic AI. The topics are grouped into core areas, each with a designated weight to highlight its importance.

